W = as_adjacency_matrix(g)

# "dgCMatrix""matrix"
W = as.matrix(W)                  


# 
converg = FALSE
old.nrow = nrow(W)

while(!converg){
  # W
  d = colSums(W)
  to.keep = which(d >= 3)
  # 3
  if(old.nrow == length(to.keep)){
    converg = TRUE
  }
  old.nrow = length(to.keep)
  W = W[to.keep,to.keep]
}

g_core = graph_from_adjacency_matrix(W, mode = "undirected")

#
